<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>JubiPago - Nuevo Ahorro</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 30px;
    }
    
    .logo-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    
    .logo {
      width: 180px;
    }
    
    h2 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .info-box {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    
    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    
    input[type="text"],
    input[type="number"] {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px;
      border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }
    
    input[type="text"]:focus,
    input[type="number"]:focus {
      border-color: #3498db;
      outline: none;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .btn-secondary {
      background-color: #95a5a6;
      color: white;
    }
    
    .error-message {
      color: #e74c3c;
      margin: 5px 0;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo-container">
      <img src="/images/jubipago.png" alt="JubiPago Logo" class="logo">
    </div>
    
    <h2>CREAR NUEVO AHORRO</h2>
    
    <div class="info-box">
      <p>El ahorro funciona separando un monto de su cantidad disponible de dinero. Este monto queda inutilizable hasta que se decida retirar.</p>
      <p>Una vez que se decida retirar el dinero del ahorro, el mismo volver√° a estar disponible para su uso.</p>
    </div>
    
    <h3>Ingrese el monto que desea ahorrar</h3>
    
    <form action="/savings" method="post">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="saving_name">Nombre del ahorro</label>
        <input type="text" id="saving_name" name="saving[name]" placeholder="Ej: Vacaciones, Auto nuevo..." required>
      </div>
      
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="saving_amount">Monto</label>
        <input type="number" id="saving_amount" name="saving[amount]" min="0.01" step="0.01" placeholder="0.00" required>
      </div>
      
      <% if @saving && @saving.errors.any? %>
        <div style="color: #e74c3c; margin-bottom: 15px;">
          <% @saving.errors.full_messages.each do |message| %>
            <div class="error-message"><%= message %></div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Siguiente</button>
      <a href="/savings" class="btn btn-secondary">Cancelar</a>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>